never returned in ten years.)

9
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,320
(But he is the only son.)

10
00:00:31,679 --> 00:00:34,200
(Would Lu Changhe really kill him?)

11
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:37,600
Being out of your sight
is a kind of disappearance.

12
00:00:37,759 --> 00:00:40,039
Being white bones is another.

13
00:00:40,679 --> 00:00:43,399
Mr. Lu, which one do you want?

14
00:00:43,799 --> 00:00:45,159
Miss Mu, you are so smart.

15
00:00:45,759 --> 00:00:47,000
You must know what I mean.

16
00:00:48,079 --> 00:00:49,280
No matter which one you want,

17
00:00:49,439 --> 00:00:50,560
the risk for me is enormous.

18
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:52,600
So,

19
00:00:53,439 --> 00:00:54,159
Mr. Lu,

20
00:00:55,039 --> 00:00:57,039
I need your promise.

21
00:00:58,159 --> 00:01:01,799
I need your full support and trust.

22
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,359
I'm a good choice.

23
00:01:06,519 --> 00:01:08,200
Otherwise, you wouldn't have come.

24
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:09,159
Mr. Lu.

25
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:11,480
Take your time to consider.

26
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:16,959
Alright.

27
00:01:28,159 --> 00:01:29,680
Mr. Lu has been seen with that dancer.

28
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:30,879
