to fight me over Changhe?

30
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,439
She must have a death wish!

31
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,879
You wench, open the door!

32
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:41,920
Open the door!

33
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,079
I know you are in there!

34
00:01:43,359 --> 00:01:45,359
Open the door!

35
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,680
Open the door!

36
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:49,719
Do you hear me?

37
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:53,920
You wench.

38
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:56,280
I'm t-t-too nice to you, huh?

39
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,000
Watch your mouth.

40
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,159
If you dare hurt me,

41
00:01:59,239 --> 00:02:01,760
