42
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:04,000
H-hey, don't be rash!

43
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,719
You should tell that to yourself.

44
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:07,719
If you keep it up,

45
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,280
