66
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,280
Related to me?

67
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:49,919
Then I'll deal with it myself.

68
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,080
How dare you?

69
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:55,919
