75
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:19,480
Your father will come in at any time.

76
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:21,399
He is not my father.

77
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,360
What?

78
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,199
Miss Mu.

79
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,519
Hold on.

80
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,399
Come again?

81
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,040
He is not my father.

82
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,079
He's just a monster

83
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,759
who looks exactly like my father.

84
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:37,800
My parents, and your mother,

85
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:39,800
were all killed by him.

86
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,480
Ridiculous.

87
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,800
If that's the case,

88
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:46,720
why don't you kill him?

89
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,040
Because I haven't figured out

90
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,199
his true identity.

91
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,600
To outsiders,

92
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:53,680
killing him would be patricide.

93
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:58,600
Miss Mu.

94
00:04:59,319 --> 00:05:00,399
I've thought it through.

95
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:02,600
I can give you a promise.

96
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,040
Make him leave.

97
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:15,360
Alright, Mr. Lu!

98
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,199
Miss Mu, what did you say?

99
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,680
I didn't catch that.

100
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,720
Miss Mu.

101
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:37,600
May I come in?

102
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:42,399
Make him leave!

103
00:05:49,759 --> 00:05:50,600
Mr. Lu.

104
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,240
