105
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:53,600
I couldn't see you in person.

106
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,560
What promise will you give me?

107
00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:57,519
Marry you.

108
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:58,519
Okay?

109
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:01,639
Reject him.

110
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:17,800
Glad to work with you, Mr. Lu.

111
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:21,279
Then I'll await your good news.

112
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,519
Young Master.

113
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:26,800
You said he's not your father.

114
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,399
