115
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,160
I can't believe you.

116
00:06:37,679 --> 00:06:39,231
(Haicheng Station)

117
00:06:43,319 --> 00:06:44,399
Leave Haicheng immediately.

118
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:46,959
